				<td colspan="2"><span>Alright, this is a topic I've been somewhat uncertain of for a while and want to get straightend out to be sure I'm not wasting my usefulness here...
<br />
I understand there's haste and overhaste, and an overall cap, but my question is, do various overhastes stack?
<br />
Main reason I ask is because more often than not on raids I'm put in the ranger group as a battery. Quite frequently I have no need to add resists, so I go all out on haste and atk, doing Warsong of Zek/Call of the Muse/Warsong of Vah Shir/Composition of Ervaj.
<br />

<br />
To the point- Am I wasting my use by attempting to throw on more than one overhaste, or is there still benefit?</span></td>
